&#13;
Finally, I did an enhanced version of this useful extension:&#13;
&#13;
- All in french,&#13;
- Works under Linux with .sql.gz extension of the dump files,&#13;
- As many dump as you want per hour&#13;
- Some cosmetic enhancements&#13;
- Some modifications about the presentation of the information.&#13;
&#13;
2 archives are available at the end of this french documentation:&#13;
&#13;
http://luxpopuli.fr/eZ-Publish/Extensions/eZ-Publish-i-bpce_backupbdd-i-sauvegarde-automatique-de-la-base-de-donnees&#13;
&#13;
One archive for PHP4&#13;
An other one for PHP5&#13;
